metadata.name: Radius
metadata.description:
Radius -  2022 - Coloured epoxy  - 11 x 11 cm

A straight line extending from the center of a circle from the focus to any point of a curve.

By purchasing the digital version of Radius, the real version will be send to you. Radius has 1 integrated hole which makes it suitable for direct application on a wall.

Radius is the pair of Inradius and completes the coupled work.
